- Where are we going?
- ( canister fires )

29:43.448 --> 29:45.109
( rasping )

29:45.284 --> 29:47.775
Stop. Right now.

29:47.953 --> 29:49.818
On the ground!
On the ground! Stop!

29:49.997 --> 29:52.409
- ( gunshots )
- ( crowd screams )

