( helicopter blades
whirring )

30:03.010 --> 30:05.467
- ( woman screams )
- Man: Go! Go, man! Let's go!

30:18.108 --> 30:20.019
- Where are we going?
- This way.

30:25.198 --> 30:27.655
-( people shouting )
- ( sirens wailing)

30:32.039 --> 30:35.156
- Okay?
- ( woman speaks Spanish )

30:35.334 --> 30:37.666
- Thing of beauty.
- Looks good, looks good.

30:37.836 --> 30:38.996
Man:
Kick this wall down!

30:39.171 --> 30:41.412
Man #2: Man, what's
going on out here?

30:41.590 --> 30:44.206
Take the side.
Take the side.

30:44.384 --> 30:45.499
Go to your right.

30:45.677 --> 30:47.008
( people shouting )

30:47.179 --> 30:48.840
Chris:
Jeez!

30:53.518 --> 30:56.385
Excuse me, sir.
Can we come in, please?

30:56.563 --> 30:58.224
We're closed.

30:58.398 --> 31:00.480
Please, it's not safe out here.
I mean, it's dangerous.

31:00.650 --> 31:01.730
Go to the police.

31:01.902 --> 31:03.392
No, I think
they're the danger.

31:03.570 --> 31:04.901
I mean, they're not
letting anyone leave.

31:05.072 --> 31:06.482
We just need somewhere
to ride it out.

31:06.656 --> 31:07.645
Please. Please?

31:07.824 --> 31:09.530
( speaks Spanish )

31:11.495 --> 31:14.032
Please.

31:14.206 --> 31:15.195
Okay, come in.

31:15.374 --> 31:17.581
Thank you.
Thank you.

31:17.751 --> 31:21.835
- ( shouting continues)
- ( horn honking )

31:22.005 --> 31:25.418
( crowd shouting,
cheering )

31:28.053 --> 31:30.260
Do you have a back door?
Access to the alley?

31:30.430 --> 31:32.386
- There is no other door.
- Travis, please.

31:32.557 --> 31:34.843
Woman:
Hey, hey.

31:35.018 --> 31:36.428
- ( man speaks Spanish )
- Liza: Travis,

31:36.603 --> 31:37.683
- this is their home.
- ( woman speaks Spanish )

31:37.854 --> 31:39.230
Do you have access
to the roof?

31:39.398 --> 31:41.184
Travis, can you please
not go in there?

31:41.358 --> 31:43.394
We can see
what's coming there.

31:43.568 --> 31:45.433
You will be fine in there.

31:45.612 --> 31:47.773
I think it'll be safer if we
stay away from the front door.

31:47.948 --> 31:50.189
No, I think you will
be safer in there.

31:50.367 --> 31:52.107
Papa, I thought
you were locking up.

31:52.285 --> 31:55.197
( speaks Spanish )

31:55.372 --> 31:57.283
- Are you okay?
- We're fine.

31:57.457 --> 31:59.573
- Who are you?
- |'m-- I'm sorry.

31:59.751 --> 32:01.457
I'm sorry. I'm Travis.
This is my family.

32:01.628 --> 32:04.040
We just need somewhere to ride
it out, and then we'll go.

32:04.214 --> 32:05.954
- ( siren wailing)
- ( distant shouting )

32:07.300 --> 32:09.291
(distant banging )

32:09.469 --> 32:12.632
It's okay, Papa.
Please, have a seat in there.

32:13.890 --> 32:15.221
Thank you, thank you.
I'm sorry.

32:15.392 --> 32:16.882
Sorry.

32:17.060 --> 32:18.561
Just take a seat.

32:18.728 --> 32:19.979
Thank you.

32:20.147 --> 32:23.981
( both speaking Spanish )

32:30.490 --> 32:31.946
Woman on radio:
LA County health officials

32:32.117 --> 32:34.654
recommend Angelinos
stay inside.

32:34.828 --> 32:36.819
If you don't
need to travel, don't.

32:36.997 --> 32:39.830
If you must leave your house,
take precautions.

32:40.000 --> 32:41.991
Local neighborhood watch
programs are being established

32:42.169 --> 32:43.875
in many neighborhoods
throughout the city...

32:44.045 --> 32:45.581
( radio turns off)

32:51.845 --> 32:54.928
You can stay with us, Tobias,
until this is over.

32:56.516 --> 32:58.427
This doesn't end.

32:58.602 --> 33:00.558
There's room.
It's safe.

33:00.729 --> 33:03.562
You gotta take care
ofyourson.

33:07.777 --> 33:09.608
I'll be okay.

33:10.655 --> 33:12.156
You?

33:14.367 --> 33:16.028
Yeah.

33:29.716 --> 33:32.207
(car approaching )

33:52.322 --> 33:55.314
-( praying in Spanish)
- ( distant shouting )

34:06.753 --> 34:08.744
( car alarm blaring )

34:10.674 --> 34:13.256
Thank you.

34:13.426 --> 34:15.508
Thank my wife.

34:18.765 --> 34:22.098
( distant tires screech )

34:22.269 --> 34:24.180
This is insane.

34:24.354 --> 34:26.515
Chris, get away
from the window.

34:28.358 --> 34:29.393
Can't make anything out.

34:29.568 --> 34:31.183
You don't wanna see
anything out there.

34:31.361 --> 34:33.773
Okay?
Just, come on, step away.

34:33.947 --> 34:37.280
Sit down.
Read something.

34:37.450 --> 34:40.613
(siren wailing)

34:47.961 --> 34:50.293
What do you know?

34:50.463 --> 34:52.203
What have you seen?

34:52.382 --> 34:54.088
( distant shattering )

34:54.259 --> 34:56.796
- I've seen what people do.
- ( engine roars)

34:56.970 --> 34:59.302
What they don't do.

35:00.974 --> 35:03.590
- It doesn't make sense.
- ( glass shatters )

35:05.312 --> 35:07.803
They don't die, Liza.
They...

35:09.316 --> 35:10.556
( glass shatters )

35:10.734 --> 35:13.396
- ...come back.
- ( fire crackling )

35:17.449 --> 35:19.656
Gotta get far away
from what's outside.

35:19.826 --> 35:23.068
( car alarm blaring )

35:23.246 --> 35:24.656
All of us.

35:26.916 --> 35:28.622
( man shouting )

35:28.793 --> 35:31.330
( officer on P.A., indistinct)

35:31.504 --> 35:33.005
(tires squealing,
engine rewing )

35:33.173 --> 35:36.336
(sirens wailing,
horn honking )

35:39.512 --> 35:42.094
