- Shut the door.

35:45.018 --> 35:46.508
How's your brother?

35:46.686 --> 35:49.268
Never better.

35:49.439 --> 35:51.475
He went grand mal on me.

35:51.650 --> 35:53.561
I'm sorry.

35:55.528 --> 35:58.019
- Travis call?
- No.

36:11.461 --> 36:13.702
(pills rattling)

36:23.223 --> 36:25.009
We ration those.

36:25.183 --> 36:27.720
Oxy? Oxy's good.
How much?

36:27.894 --> 36:29.725
It's enough to get us
to the desert.

36:29.896 --> 36:32.137
And then what?

36:36.736 --> 36:38.818
Hey.
(snaps fingers)

36:38.988 --> 36:40.979
She tried to leave.

36:42.534 --> 36:43.740
Yeah.

36:43.910 --> 36:45.901
I stopped her.

36:54.254 --> 36:55.585
(tapping )

36:55.755 --> 36:57.370
Alicia:
Hey, Matt, it's me again.

36:57.549 --> 37:00.086
Can you give me a call?
I wanna know how you're doing.

37:37.422 --> 37:41.131
(crying )
No. No, God.

37:46.473 --> 37:48.589
(cell phone ringing)

37:54.272 --> 37:56.137
- Travis?
- Maddy. Maddy?

37:56.316 --> 37:59.149
- Travis? Hi.
- You can hear me?

37:59.319 --> 38:00.980
Yeah, baby, where are you?
Are you okay?

38:01.154 --> 38:04.271
Yeah, no, we're good.
I found Chris. He's safe.

38:04.449 --> 38:06.735
Where are you?
You okay?

38:06.910 --> 38:10.573
Yeah, we're okay.
Can you come home?

38:10.747 --> 38:13.113
We're stuck.
The freeway's jammed,

38:13.291 --> 38:15.156
and highway patrol's
figuring it out.

38:15.335 --> 38:17.121
l, um...

38:17.295 --> 38:19.832
Well, where are you?
You're at Liza's?

38:20.006 --> 38:22.338
No, no.
We're waiting in a shop.

38:22.509 --> 38:24.841
|-- how's Nick?
Is he okay?

38:25.011 --> 38:26.751
Did you find him the meds?

38:26.930 --> 38:29.171
Uh, yeah.
Uh...

38:30.517 --> 38:32.599
I got him enough,
you know, to wean him off.

38:32.769 --> 38:35.476
I mean, to take him to the
desert and just wean him off.

38:35.647 --> 38:36.978
- ( explosion )
- Oh, shit.

38:37.148 --> 38:39.013
Madison: Wait, Travis,
what was that?

38:39.192 --> 38:41.103
- Tell me what that was.
- No, it's okay. It's okay.

38:41.277 --> 38:42.483
Yeah, I'm fine.
I'm fine.

38:42.654 --> 38:44.485
Look, Maddy,
I want you to go.

38:44.656 --> 38:46.863
Go to the desert, now.
Don't wait.

38:47.033 --> 38:50.321
No, I'm gonna wait for you.
I'm gonna wait for you.

38:50.495 --> 38:52.326
Okay, I don't know
how long we're gonna be.

38:52.497 --> 38:54.362
Just go ahead. We'll catch up.
We'll find you, okay?

38:54.541 --> 38:56.372
No, Travis, just-- no--

38:56.543 --> 38:58.704
- ( gunshots )
- Whoa! Travis?

38:58.878 --> 39:01.210
- Maddy?
- ( screaming, shattering )

39:01.381 --> 39:03.497
Officer over P.A.
By order of the LAPD,

39:03.675 --> 39:06.883
you must clear
the streets now.

39:08.137 --> 39:09.968
( crickets chirping )

39:16.563 --> 39:18.224
( beeps )

39:21.526 --> 39:23.391
(sighs)

39:28.658 --> 39:31.320
( sighs, sniffles )

39:35.832 --> 39:37.663
What the hell happened?

39:39.377 --> 39:41.242
Mom?

39:43.256 --> 39:45.417
Mom, are you okay?

39:48.386 --> 39:49.751
Mom.

39:49.929 --> 39:52.386
"Wait For Me" playing

39:54.225 --> 39:56.762
( static hissing )

40:01.733 --> 40:04.725
(woman vocalizing )

40:22.045 --> 40:24.787
J‘ I'm gonna ask you
to look away... J‘

40:24.964 --> 40:27.546
- ( crowd shouting )
- J‘ Mm-mm J‘

40:27.717 --> 40:32.256
J‘ I love my hands,
but it hurts to pray... J‘

40:32.430 --> 40:33.590
(touch-tones beeping )

40:33.765 --> 40:37.053
J‘ The life l have
isn't what I've seen J‘

40:39.479 --> 40:42.812
J‘ The sky's not blue
and the field's not green... J‘

40:48.947 --> 40:51.063
(sighs)

40:53.993 --> 40:55.654
Dead again?

40:56.996 --> 40:58.497
Phone lines
keep going off and on.

40:58.665 --> 41:00.326
Power cuts out.

41:02.335 --> 41:05.702
Tell me.
What's going on?

41:08.925 --> 41:10.005
( distant woman screams )

41:10.176 --> 41:11.837
Oh, God.

41:12.011 --> 41:14.172
- ( screaming continues)
- Oh, my God.

41:14.347 --> 41:16.338
(man grunting)

41:16.516 --> 41:17.676
( Mrs. Cruz screaming )

41:17.850 --> 41:19.135
Don't look.
Don't look.

41:19.310 --> 41:21.767
Mom, Mr. Dawson's
hurting them.

41:21.938 --> 41:24.850
( screaming )
Get off!

41:27.485 --> 41:29.646
No. Alicia!

41:29.821 --> 41:31.106
- ( screaming escalates )
- No.

41:31.280 --> 41:35.023
What are you doing?
Mom. Mom!

41:37.286 --> 41:41.199
(woman praying in Spanish )

41:52.510 --> 41:55.547
( prayer continues )

42:00.393 --> 42:02.884
( distant siren wailing )

42:19.328 --> 42:22.161
